{"article_id":"cUNBHIlo0Pz4TaW2","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"Under cross examination at the tax evasion and bank fraud trial of his ex-boss Paul Manafort ,","depth":7},{"id":1,"text":"Gates struggled to give clear answers","depth":7},{"id":2,"text":"A former campaign aide to Donald Trump lived a \" secret life \"","depth":10},{"id":3,"text":"including an extramarital affair in London ,","depth":10},{"id":4,"text":"a court heard on Tuesday .","depth":9},{"id":5,"text":"Rick Gates , under cross examination at the tax evasion and bank fraud trial of his former boss Paul Manafort , admitted","depth":10},{"id":6,"text":"that he had \" another relationship \"","depth":11},{"id":7,"text":"involving first-class flights and luxury hotels ,","depth":11},{"id":8,"text":"but denied","depth":10},{"id":9,"text":"these were funded with money","depth":11},{"id":10,"text":"embezzled from Manafort .","depth":11},{"id":11,"text":"Manafort ex-business partner Rick Gates testifies","depth":9},{"id":12,"text":"they committed crimes together","depth":9},{"id":13,"text":"Read more","depth":8},{"id":14,"text":"Manafort , a former Trump campaign chairman , has pleaded not guilty to 18 counts of bank and tax fraud and failing to disclose foreign bank accounts .","depth":7},{"id":15,"text":"His defence team is seeking to pin the blame on Gates ,","depth":9},{"id":16,"text":"who","depth":11},{"id":17,"text":"they say","depth":11},{"id":18,"text":"was responsible for day-to-day operations of the business .","depth":10},{"id":19,"text":"In a dramatic moment before the jury , Manafort ' s defence counsel , Kevin Downing , put it to the government ' s star witness :","depth":9},{"id":20,"text":"\" There ' s another life , right , the other Rick Gates ?","depth":10},{"id":21,"text":"The secret Rick Gates ? \"","depth":10},{"id":22,"text":"Play Video 4:47","depth":9},{"id":23,"text":"Russia inquiry :","depth":10},{"id":24,"text":"how Trump 's inner circle could bring him down - video explainer","depth":10},{"id":25,"text":"Gates ,","depth":12},{"id":26,"text":"who is 46 and married ,","depth":12},{"id":27,"text":"admitted :","depth":11},{"id":28,"text":"\" There was a period in my life , about 10 years ago ,","depth":11},{"id":29,"text":"when I had a relationship , yes . \"","depth":11},{"id":30,"text":"With a nod to linguistic differences for what Americans refer to as an apartment , Downing pressed :","depth":10},{"id":31,"text":"\" As part of your secret life did you maintain a flat","depth":12},{"id":32,"text":"- is that what they call it ? -","depth":12},{"id":33,"text":"in London ? \"","depth":11},{"id":34,"text":"Paul Manafort trial :","depth":9},{"id":35,"text":"prosecutors seek to paint picture of luxe lifestyle","depth":9},{"id":36,"text":"Read more","depth":9},{"id":37,"text":"Gates acknowledged","depth":11},{"id":38,"text":"that he did for two months","depth":12},{"id":39,"text":"and that he took first class flights","depth":13},{"id":40,"text":"and stayed in \" fancy hotels \" around Europe ,","depth":13},{"id":41,"text":"but said","depth":12},{"id":42,"text":"the money came from bonuses rather than illicit gains .","depth":12},{"id":43,"text":"\" I had a period of time","depth":13},{"id":44,"text":"when I had another relationship , \"","depth":13},{"id":45,"text":"he added .","depth":12},{"id":46,"text":"As well as being a senior aide on Trump ' s election campaign ,","depth":6},{"id":47,"text":"Gates served as the deputy chairman of the US president ' s inaugural committee .","depth":6},{"id":48,"text":"On Tuesday , he admitted","depth":8},{"id":49,"text":"it was possible he had sought to cheat the committee with false expenses claims .","depth":8},{"id":50,"text":"\" Did you submit personal expenses to the inaugural committee for reimbursement ? \"","depth":10},{"id":51,"text":"Downing asked .","depth":10},{"id":52,"text":"Gates appeared nervous on the witness stand at the court in Alexandria , Virginia ,","depth":12},{"id":53,"text":"blinking frequently ,","depth":13},{"id":54,"text":"his throat apparently dry","depth":14},{"id":55,"text":"as he spoke .","depth":14},{"id":56,"text":"He frequently used the phrases","depth":12},{"id":57,"text":"\" It ' s possible \"","depth":14},{"id":58,"text":"and \" I don ' t recall \"","depth":14},{"id":59,"text":"as Downing challenged him about inconsistencies in testimony","depth":14},{"id":60,"text":"he gave to the special counsel ' s office .","depth":14},{"id":61,"text":"\" When did you start providing false and misleading information to the special counsel ' s office ? \"","depth":12},{"id":62,"text":"the defence counsel asked bluntly .","depth":12},{"id":63,"text":"Gates struggled so badly","depth":15},{"id":64,"text":"to give a straight answer","depth":15},{"id":65,"text":"that eventually Judge T S Ellis III was forced to intervene .","depth":14},{"id":66,"text":"\" Did you provide false information","depth":15},{"id":67,"text":"or did you have a bad memory ? \"","depth":15},{"id":68,"text":"he asked .","depth":14},{"id":69,"text":"Gates finally admitted","depth":14},{"id":70,"text":"that he had provided false information prior","depth":15},{"id":71,"text":"to striking a plea agreement .","depth":15},{"id":72,"text":"\" I did , to one count , your honour , \"","depth":14},{"id":73,"text":"he said .","depth":14},{"id":74,"text":"He has already admitted embezzling some funds from Manafort .","depth":9},{"id":75,"text":"Downing pressed him on the specifics of their business relationship :","depth":12},{"id":76,"text":"which payments to Gates were authorised","depth":13},{"id":77,"text":"and which were not .","depth":13},{"id":78,"text":"Regarding a trading company","depth":15},{"id":79,"text":"Manafort had started with a partner in 2011 ,","depth":15},{"id":80,"text":"he asked with deep scepticism :","depth":14},{"id":81,"text":"\" You ' re asking the jury to believe","depth":14},{"id":82,"text":"Mr Manafort authorised another $ 250,000 as a bonus ? \"","depth":14},{"id":83,"text":"Why is Paul Manafort risking it all","depth":13},{"id":84,"text":"to face Mueller charges in court ?","depth":13},{"id":85,"text":"Read more","depth":10},{"id":86,"text":"Downing wondered aloud","depth":10},{"id":87,"text":"why Gates had shown \" perfect recollection \" during examination by the government","depth":11},{"id":88,"text":"but was now much less precise under cross-examination by Manafort ' s defence .","depth":11},{"id":89,"text":"He challenged the witness :","depth":11},{"id":90,"text":"\" Have they","depth":14},{"id":91,"text":"[ the special counsel ' s office ]","depth":14},{"id":92,"text":"confronted you with so many lies","depth":13},{"id":93,"text":"you can ' t remember any of it ? \"","depth":12},{"id":94,"text":"Gates testified","depth":11},{"id":95,"text":"that he stole from Manafort","depth":12},{"id":96,"text":"because he was living beyond his means .","depth":12},{"id":97,"text":"Downing asked :","depth":10},{"id":98,"text":"\" Was it for your secret life ? \"","depth":10},{"id":99,"text":"The witness replied defensively :","depth":10},{"id":100,"text":"\" It ' s not a secret life .","depth":11},{"id":101,"text":"It went to an account","depth":12},{"id":102,"text":"my wife knew about . \"","depth":12},{"id":103,"text":"Though he has at times seemed evasive under cross-examination ,","depth":9},{"id":104,"text":"Gates insisted","depth":10},{"id":105,"text":"that he now acknowledges his mistake","depth":12},{"id":106,"text":"and is taking responsibility for it ,","depth":12},{"id":107,"text":"whereas Manafort is not .","depth":11},{"id":108,"text":"But Downing challenged again :","depth":9},{"id":109,"text":"\" After all the lies","depth":12},{"id":110,"text":"you ' ve told","depth":12},{"id":111,"text":"and fraud","depth":12},{"id":112,"text":"you ' ve committed ,","depth":12},{"id":113,"text":"you expect this jury to believe you ? \"","depth":10},{"id":114,"text":"Earlier on Tuesday , the prosecution had continued to question Gates ,","depth":7},{"id":115,"text":"who described","depth":8},{"id":116,"text":"how millions of dollars were allegedly funneled from entities","depth":9},{"id":117,"text":"controlled by Ukrainian businessmen into Manafort ' s shell companies in Cyprus .","depth":9},{"id":118,"text":"Although the allegations of collusion between Donald Trump and Russia are not at issue in this trial ,","depth":7},{"id":119,"text":"any significant blows to the government ' s case are likely to be seized on by the president ' s defenders ,","depth":9},{"id":120,"text":"including conservative media ,","depth":9},{"id":121,"text":"to support his contention","depth":9},{"id":122,"text":"that Mueller ' s investigation is a \" rigged witch-hunt \" .","depth":9},{"id":123,"text":"Paul Manafort lawyers want mention of Trump banned in Virginia trial","depth":5},{"id":124,"text":"Read more","depth":4},{"id":125,"text":"Gates pleaded guilty in February","depth":5},{"id":126,"text":"and agreed to cooperate with prosecutors under a deal","depth":6},{"id":127,"text":"that could lead to a reduced sentence .","depth":6},{"id":128,"text":"On Monday , he testified","depth":7},{"id":129,"text":"that he helped Manafort file false tax returns and hide his foreign bank accounts .","depth":7},{"id":130,"text":"He was aware","depth":8},{"id":131,"text":"that Manafort was acting as an unregistered foreign agent in lobbying for Ukraine ,","depth":8},{"id":132,"text":"he said .","depth":7},{"id":133,"text":"On Tuesday , the court was shown a series of emails , contracts and what prosecutor Greg Andres referred to as \" fake invoices \" ,","depth":7},{"id":134,"text":"in which Gates altered the template","depth":8},{"id":135,"text":"to show the name of a shell company instead of Manafort ' s .","depth":8},{"id":136,"text":"This was a way","depth":8},{"id":137,"text":"to decrease Manafort ' s taxable income ,","depth":8},{"id":138,"text":"added Gates ,","depth":8},{"id":139,"text":"who did not report the money to Manafort ' s bookkeeper or accountants .","depth":8},{"id":140,"text":"Manafort ' s political work included advising Viktor Yanukovych on policy","depth":10},{"id":141,"text":"after he won the Ukrainian presidency ,","depth":10},{"id":142,"text":"Gates said .","depth":9},{"id":143,"text":"\" Mr Manafort worked with the local political officials","depth":9},{"id":144,"text":"and helped implement policy initiatives","depth":10},{"id":145,"text":"based on the campaign promises . \"","depth":10},{"id":146,"text":"For this Manafort was paid $ 4m a year , in quarterly payments of $ 1m ,","depth":9},{"id":147,"text":"Gates recalled ,","depth":9},{"id":148,"text":"though at some point the currency switched from US dollars to Euros .","depth":8},{"id":149,"text":"His consultancy work also included \" Engage Ukraine \" , an effort","depth":7},{"id":150,"text":"to help Ukraine join the European Union .","depth":7},{"id":151,"text":"Government lawyers have previously referred to Yanukovych as Manafort ' s \" golden goose \" .","depth":5},{"id":152,"text":"After Yanukovych lost power in 2014 ,","depth":8},{"id":153,"text":"\" I would say","depth":9},{"id":154,"text":"it decreased the income stream \" ,","depth":9},{"id":155,"text":"Gates ,","depth":9},{"id":156,"text":"wearing a blue suit ,","depth":9},{"id":157,"text":"told the court matter-of-factly .","depth":8},{"id":158,"text":"He added","depth":7},{"id":159,"text":"Manafort worked for a time for the Opposition Bloc , the party","depth":9},{"id":160,"text":"that replaced Yanukovych ' s Party of Regions ,","depth":9},{"id":161,"text":"but it was out of power","depth":9},{"id":162,"text":"and so \" income streams were more difficult to come by \" .","depth":9},{"id":163,"text":"By July 2015 ,","depth":9},{"id":164,"text":"the court heard ,","depth":9},{"id":165,"text":"Manafort was struggling financially .","depth":8},{"id":166,"text":"Andres asked :","depth":9},{"id":167,"text":"\" Was he having trouble paying his bills ? \"","depth":9},{"id":168,"text":"Gates replied :","depth":9},{"id":169,"text":"\" He was . \"","depth":9},{"id":170,"text":"Gates said","depth":7},{"id":171,"text":"he and Manafort turned to a Cypriot lawyer ,","depth":9},{"id":172,"text":"whom he referred to in court as \" Dr K \" ,","depth":9},{"id":173,"text":"who set up bank accounts and shell companies on Manafort ' s behalf","depth":9},{"id":174,"text":"and \" handled everything \" .","depth":9},{"id":175,"text":"FBI investigates Russian-linked Cyprus bank","depth":4},{"id":176,"text":"accused of money laundering","depth":4},{"id":177,"text":"Read more","depth":3},{"id":178,"text":"When an individual sets up an entity in Cyprus ,","depth":6},{"id":179,"text":"Gates explained ,","depth":6},{"id":180,"text":"their name does not appear on any of the paperwork .","depth":5},{"id":181,"text":"He said of Manafort :","depth":5},{"id":182,"text":"\" I believe","depth":6},{"id":183,"text":"he understood","depth":7},{"id":184,"text":"his name would not be represented ,","depth":8},{"id":185,"text":"nor would mine . \"","depth":8},{"id":186,"text":"As Manafort came under pressure","depth":7},{"id":187,"text":"to pay his bills ,","depth":7},{"id":188,"text":"he was forced to seek loans ,","depth":6},{"id":189,"text":"the court heard .","depth":5},{"id":190,"text":"Gates said","depth":6},{"id":191,"text":"he was responsible","depth":7},{"id":192,"text":"for collecting all relevant documents for the loan applications .","depth":7},{"id":193,"text":"Andres asked him :","depth":6},{"id":194,"text":"\" Did you provide false information to the banks ? '","depth":6}],"relations":[{"parent":389,"left":369,"right":388,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":369,"left":319,"right":368,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":319,"left":308,"right":318,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":308,"left":240,"right":307,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":240,"left":208,"right":239,"relation":"